<form>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="height">Height [ft]:</label>
        <input type="text" id="height" name="height" value="{{ height }}" />
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="surfaces">Landing surface:</label>
        <select id="surfaces" name="surfaces">
            {{selectOptions surfaces selected=surface valueAttr='key' labelAttr='label'}}
        </select>
    </div>

    <p>
        In a clear fall of more than 15 feet, Acrobatics or Dodge can be used to moderate the fall, by landing on one’s feet rather than
        one’s head.
    </p>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="clear">Clear fall:</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="clear" name="clear" value="{{ clear }}" data-dtype="Boolean" checked />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="skills">Skill:</label>
        <select id="skills" name="skills">
            {{selectOptions skills selected=skill valueAttr='key' labelAttr='key'}}
        </select>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="modifier">Modifier:</label>
        <input type="text" id="modifier" name="modifier" value="{{ modifier }}" />
    </div>

    <p>
        A character may be able to stop falling by grabbing protrusions, bushes, etc. This rarely stops the fall, but may slow it and reduce
        landing impact.
    </p>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="grabbing">Grabbing:</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="grabbing" name="grabbing" value="{{ grabbing }}" data-dtype="Boolean" />
    </div>
</form>
